245
00:16:50,154 --> 00:16:52,490
- No, you don't.
- You're the best, man.

246
00:16:52,616 --> 00:16:55,035
Come on, Benny, man.
The kid is...

247
00:16:55,160 --> 00:16:58,790
a L-7 weenie.

248
00:16:58,957 --> 00:17:02,503
