253
00:17:17,773 --> 00:17:20,068
Now, how come
he don't get to be?

254
00:17:20,193 --> 00:17:22,279
- 'Cause he's a geek, man.
- He can't catch.

255
00:17:22,321 --> 00:17:25,408
Man, base up,
you blockheads.

256
00:17:30,915 --> 00:17:34,086
Smalls, you take
left center, okay?

257
00:17:34,169 --> 00:17:37,173
Okay. Um, where
