258
00:17:39,259 --> 00:17:41,178
It's over there, man.

259
00:17:47,645 --> 00:17:49,564
Here?

260
00:17:51,776 --> 00:17:53,653
That's left.
I said left center.

261
00:17:54,863 --> 00:17:57,116
Okay. Right.

262
00:17:57,199 --> 00:17:59,118
Here?

263
00:18:01,997 --> 00:18:04,542
Come on, Benny, man.

264
00:18:04,626 --> 00:18:08,255
He's never gonna catch the ball anyway.
Let's just play.

265
00:18:10,174 --> 00:18:13,929
- What a jerk.
- Yeah-Yeah, get two.

266
00:18:17,184 --> 00:18:19,270
Come on!
Throw it in here, Bertram!

267
00:18:21,689 --> 00:18:24,276
- Nice.
- Wow!

268
00:18:24,359 --> 00:18:26,237
Good job!

269
00:18:28,698 --> 00:18:31,494
- Hey, Smalls, throw it to second.
- Okay.

270
00:18:32,871 --> 00:18:35,082
[ Gasps ]

271
00:18:35,207 --> 00:18:39,254
- Come on, Benny.
He's never gonna catch it.
- He's not gonna catch it.

272
00:18:39,421 --> 00:18:41,674
[ Grunting ]

273
00:18:41,715 --> 00:18:44,636
Oh! I told you, Benny.
We told you.

274
00:18:46,930 --> 00:18:48,850
[Dog Growling]

275
00:18:48,975 --> 00:18:51,061
Come on, Benny.
Why'd you do that?

276
00:18:54,732 --> 00:18:58,404
A square, Benny.
The kid's a square.

277
00:18:58,487 --> 00:19:01,408
