731
00:47:26,285 --> 00:47:28,162
Hey, hey, hey.

732
00:47:28,246 --> 00:47:31,166
I'm just trying to have
a little friendly conversation.

733
00:47:31,291 --> 00:47:34,671
Come on. You think
she'd go out with me?

734
00:47:37,299 --> 00:47:39,051
Come on.
Show me your stuff.

735
00:47:39,176 --> 00:47:41,638
- Let's see what you got.
- Hey, batter, batter, batter!

736
00:47:41,763 --> 00:47:44,433
- Take him out!
- [Boys Shouting]

737
00:48:00,621 --> 00:48:03,833
- Come on!
- Bring it in!

738
00:48:14,514 --> 00:48:17,643
- Oh! Beat ya.
- [ Shouting Continues ]

739
00:48:20,230 --> 00:48:23,025
Throw it to third!

740
00:48:53,523 --> 00:48:56,652
[Scotty Narrating ]
We were all walking on air that night.

741
00:48:56,819 --> 00:48:58,696
It had been a solid victory.

742
00:48:58,780 --> 00:49:01,116
In fact, we beat the crap
